{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1681-08_126"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À la Belle Cloris des Ambarriens"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", août 1681 [tome 9], p. 126-144."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La Violete s’est broüillée tout de nouveau avec le Muguet. C’est ce que vous apprendra la nouvelle Lettre que je vous envoye du Berger Fleuriste."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "À LA BELLE CLORIS DES AMBARRIENS."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ah, Madame, qu’il est bien vray ce qu’on m’écrivit il y a quelque temps, en ces termes !"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand l’amour est au point de son accroissement,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "On prend en bonne part ce que fait un Amant,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Dit-il, mesme une injure, il semble qu’il encense ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " Mais quand par un fâcheux retour"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "La haine regne aux Lieux où commandoit l’amour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " Qu’alors on a de défiance !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": " Un bon avis passe pour trahison,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " Un bon remede pour poison ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "On croit qu’il n’en vient rien, qui ne soit une offence."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous allez voir, aimable Cloris, une assez grande preuve de cette verité, dans cette Relation de l’Empire des Fleurs, que j’ay reçeuë d’une Lumiere de mes Amies. La voicy."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "L’un des premiers jours de cet Eté, une Roze à cent feüilles ayant assemblé le Muguet & la Violete, avec neuf autres Fleurs, pour un petit Régal qu’elle leur vouloit donner sur les belles Rives de la Jense, elles s’y virent sans témoignage de mécontentement, & partagerent en paix avec leurs Compagnes, les divertissemens de cette journée. Comme j’estois de cette Feste, j’en puis parler avec certitude."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Flore nostre grande Princesse,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Graces ses Dames d’atour,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les doux Zéphirs sa petite Noblesse,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Jeux, les Ris, qui sont les Seigneurs de sa Cour,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Estoient aussi conviez par la Roze,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Et parmy nous passerent tout le jour ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais la Feste manqua de la meilleure chose,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "On n’y vit point l’Amour."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Le hazard voulut que sur le soir, chacune de nous ayant pris party, le Muguet & la Violete se trouverent seuls, dans un petit Pré assez agreable. Ils garderent d’abord le silence ; puis le rompirent par la loüange de nos Sœurs champestres qui les environnoient ; & passant en suite de ce discours à d’autres, ils tomberent insensiblement sur leurs propres affaires."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ainsi les poursuivans de la vive étincelle,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Nos petits Moucherons"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Avant que de s’approcher d’elle,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Font quelques tours aux environs,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Puis se viennent enfin brûler à la Chandelle."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Muguet se plaignant des propos choquans que la Violete avoit tenus de luy, chez l’Iris ; & la Violete, du peu d’état que le Muguet témoignoit faire d’elle, depuis plusieurs mois. Il luy dit que les nouvelles connoissances qu’il avoit de sa Coqueterie, estoient de grands sujets de rebut. Elle luy répondit qu’un rebut qui estoit mal fondé, devoit luy tenir lieu de vangeance ; & enfin apres s’estre poussez de cette sorte pendant quelque temps, elle demanda sur quelle preuve il luy reprochoit sa Coqueterie, ajoûtant qu’il n’avoit qu’à parler & à parler sans déguisement. Le Muguet se défendit de venir à cette explication."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il connoissoit la Verité."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il sçavoit que c’est une Belle,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui quelquefois a de la cruauté."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il la trouvoit dans cette humeur cruelle"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur le sujet, dont il estoit tenté"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "De s’expliquer d’un air fidelle."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il ne sçauroit mentir, il a de la bonté,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il craignoit de déplaire ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Restoit donc à se taire."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "C’estoit son intention, & elle dura assez longtemps ; mais enfin il se rendit, tant il fut pressé par la Violete ; & la genéreuse espérance qu’elle sçauroit profiter de ce qu’il diroit, en prenant du moins mieux garde à elle à l’avenir, que par le passé, n’aida pas peu à luy ouvrir le cœur & la bouche. Apres donc luy avoir fait entendre que si elle avoit de la peine à recevoir son discours en bonne part, elle devoit penser qu’il ne tiroit à aucune conséquence, puis qu’il luy parloit sans témoins. Il luy raconta avec sa franchise ordinaire, tout ce qu’il avoit reconnu & jugé de son intrigue avec la Fleur de Pescher. La Violete n’écouta pas ce récit sans confusion. Les remarques & les penétrations du Muguet, la surprirent tout-à-fait ; & comme elle ne sçeut que luy répondre pour sa défence, elle se déchaîna contre luy d’une maniere terrible."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout ce qu’en bravant Terre & Cieux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’insolente Mégere"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Peut faire éclater de colere,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Parut avec excés, au geste & dans les yeux"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "De la brûlante Violete ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Et tout ce que l’on sçait de plus injurieux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Au prix des mots nouveaux que dit cette Coquete,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "N’est que douceur & que fleurete ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Jamais transport ne fut si furieux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Je l’ay appris d’une Fleur champestre cachée derriere un buisson, qui observoit cette Emportée, sans qu’elle s’en apperçeust. Cet orage ne se borna pas à une gresle d’injures. Elle défendit pour jamais au Muguet, l’entrée de sa retraite ; le menaça de l’insulter en toute sorte de Compagnies ; protesta de le broüiller mortellement avec le Violier ; & jura enfin ses grands Dieux, qu’elle hazarderoit encor sa réputation, & mesmes sa vie, pour se vanger de luy. Si le Muguet fut surpris d’une tempeste si extraordinaire, je le laisse à penser ; mais il le fut beaucoup d’avantage, lors qu’estant allé chez elle cinq jours apres, malgré sa défence, pour luy demander pardon de l’avoir mise en colere, persuadé qu’il devoit cette honnesteté à son Sexe, elle recommença les mesmes discours, avec la mesme fureur."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La récidive est étonnante ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais il est plus encore étonnant que le temps,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui sçait calmer la plus grande tourmente,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "N’eust rien diminué de ses transports ardens."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": " J’ay fait mon devoir, j’en suis 